            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>康卡斯特(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:CMCSA:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/CMCSA\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">CMCSA-US</a>)截至台北時間24日02:48股價下跌1.21美元，報22.32美元，跌幅5.12%，成交量27,213,389（股），盤中最高價24.01美元、最低價22.32美元。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>美股指數盤中表現</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>：-1.05%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/INX\">S&amp;P 500</a>指數：-1.38%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/IXIC\">NASDAQ</a>指數：-2.29%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>指數：-1.18%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>康卡斯特(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:CMCSA:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/CMCSA\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">CMCSA-US</a>)歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>近 1 週：+0.13%</li> <li>近 1 月：+5.38%</li> <li>近 3 月：-19.92%</li> <li>近 6 月：-19.53%</li> <li>今年以來：-21.31%</li></ul></section></main>",
